  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main objective of this study is to assess the acute effect of co-ingested vinegar on
      postprandial plasma glucose levels in type 2 diabetes patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Plasma glucose and insulin concentrations are assessed over the 2 hr period following
      ingestion of carbohydrate-rich beverage with or without added vinegar.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
